LOAN
  Offer or view loans to other countries.

SYNTAX
  loan [<loan#>]

DESCRIPTION
  The loan system allows countries to lend money to each other.
  The borrower repays with interest over time (deducted each update
  from their treasury automatically).

  Without an argument, shows all active loans involving you.
  With a loan number, shows details of that specific loan.

  To offer a loan:
    loan <cnum> <amount> <interest-rate> <duration-updates>

  The recipient can accept or decline the loan offer.  Once
  accepted, money transfers immediately and repayment begins.

EXAMPLE
  loan                      see all your active loans
  loan 3 1000 0.05 10       offer country 3 a $1000 loan, 5% rate

SEE ALSO
  nation  report  telegram
